Setup Django Project:

    Install Django:
        pip install django
    Create a new Django project:
        django-admin startproject PaytacaProject
    Navigate to the project directory:
        cd PaytacaProject
    Create a new Django app:
        python manage.py startapp PaytacaApp

Setup Django REST Framework:

    Install Django REST Framework:
        pip install djangorestframework

Setup Vue.js:

    Install Vue CLI (if not already installed):
        npm install -g @vue/cli
    Create a new Vue project:
        vue create vue_project_name
    Navigate to the Vue project directory:
        cd vue_project_name

Integrate Vue.js with Django:

    Install django-webpack-loader to integrate Vue.js with Django:

        pip install django-webpack-loader

Setup Tailwind CSS:

    Install Tailwind CSS:
        npm install tailwindcss

    Generate a tailwind.config.js file:
        npx tailwindcss init

    Install PostCSS and autoprefixer:
        npm install postcss autoprefixer

